      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HELLABELLA (5) resumes and has been in the placings at three of her four starts. Readied for this with two trial wins at Randwick, and Tim Clark is engaged. She will jump and run out of the inside barrier and sets a decent standard for the newcomers. Stablemate LOREAL BELLE (6) has been well prepared for her debut. Comes off a Randwick trial win and Rachel King sticks from that. Draws to advantage and a bold effort is on the cards.  MALUKU (7) debuts and has also trialled well at Warwick Farm. Keep onside. CANAL (2) is ex-James Cummings and has shown enough. The niggle is the 370 days off the scene, but he has three trials under his belt, and Tommy Berry is engaged.",
